  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1137646/" class="title-link">治学如逐臭</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1137646"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1011087/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1011087-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1011087/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">徐强</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-03-24"
      class="main-meta">2007-03-24 22:40:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1137646_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  治学如逐臭  ——蠹鱼笔记（9）  □/徐强  吾国学人总好追逐风气，一时之所尚，则群起而趋其途，如海上逐臭之夫，莫名所以。曾无一刹那，风气或变，而逐臭者复如故。（熊十力《十力语要•戒诸生》）  【蠹鱼案】“逐臭之夫”见《吕氏春秋》卷14《孝行览•遇合》：“人有大...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1137646/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            辽宁教育出版社1997版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1137646_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1137646_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





